description:
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen within the Endoscopy Unit, and we are looking for highly motivated, enthusiastic and dedicated individuals who are passionate about delivering excellent patient care to join our team. Your role will include patient care within the endoscopy rooms and the recovery area and assisting with the decontamination of endoscopes for the Endoscopy Service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Employees will be expected to obtain specialist and technical knowledge as well as a general understanding of policies and procedures. Competency based training will be given.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The individuals must be able to work flexibly and portray a safe, friendly and efficient service at all times.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Lead Nurse Stephanie Jones EXT 2722&lt;/p&gt;
